=<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Alerta de Dispositivo Offline</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="color-scheme" content="light dark">
  <meta name="supported-color-schemes" content="light dark">
  <style>
    :root { color-scheme: light dark; }
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; }
    .email-container { max-width: 600px; margin: auto; background-color: #f9f9f9; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 25px; }
    .header { color: #c9302c; border-bottom: 2px solid #eeeeee; padding-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 0; }
    .intro-text { font-size: 16px; color: #333333; }
    .details-box { background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; margin-top: 20px; }
    .details-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; font-size: 16px; color: #333333; }
    .list-item { padding-bottom: 10px; }
    .list-item-divider { padding-top: 10px; border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0; }
    .status-offline { color: #c9302c; font-weight: bold; }
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      .email-container { background-color: #121212 !important; border-color: #333333 !important; }
      .header { color: #ff8a80 !important; border-bottom-color: #333333 !important; }
      .intro-text, .details-list, .details-list strong { color: #e0e0e0 !important; }
      .details-box { background-color: #1e1e1e !important; border-color: #333333 !important; }
      .list-item-divider { border-top-color: #333333 !important; }
      .status-offline { color: #ff8a80 !important; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <h2 class="header">🚨 Alerta de Rede: Dispositivo Offline</h2>
    <p class="intro-text">O sistema de monitoramento detectou que o seguinte dispositivo perdeu a conexão:</p>
    <div class="details-box">
      <ul class="details-list">
        <li class="list-item"><strong>Nome do Dispositivo:</strong> {{ $json.device_name }}</li>
        <li class="list-item list-item-divider"><strong>Status Atual:</strong> <span class="status-offline">OFFLINE</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
